OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome brightness to the start
OL,6,Fthe day, and along the north coast
OL,7,Fthroughout. Otherwise it will be
OL,8,Fcloudy and mainly dry, although some
OL,9,Fpatchy rain around mainly in the south.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fclear periods. Then the rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will remain dry across all parts
OL,14,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry and
OL,17,Fcloudy, but some brightness along the
OL,18,Fnorth coast. Rain will spread east in
OL,19,Fthe afternoon and evening. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
